Formally,
\begin{itemize}
\item $V(H \oslash G) = V(H) \cup \left( \vphantom{\bigoplus} E(H) \times V(G) \setminus \{s(G),t(G)\} \right).$
\item For every edge $e=(u,v) \in E(H)$, there are $|E(G)|$ edges,
