and, for any 
$y_{n_1}\ldots y_{n_r}\in Y^*$ we set $\beta_w(z):=B_w(z)-B_w(0)$.

One defines also, for any $w=y_{n_1}\ldots y_{n_r}\in Y_0^*$ (with $b_w:=B_w(0)$) and
\begin{eqnarray*}
b'_{y_{n_k}}:=b_{y_{n_k}}&\mbox{and}&
